All that's missing is the fork. Heh.

Fork this,
Fork that,
Fork me,
Fork you,
all about forks.

There once was a fork who longed for a spoon and knife. He searched for days until, feeling deflated, he gave up hope 
and immediately began to cry. He resigned to a life of loneliness. 

An ice cream scoper noticed the sad fork. Ice cream would surely make him happy, thought the ice cream scoper.
